<br>
In both tests the attacker is a level 50 cleric, with 406 weaponskill. The weapon used is only 20% bonus, vs 35% bonus on the target's armour.<br>
The target is a level 50 merc.<br>
<br>
Unbuffed<br>
Merc stats: 157 dex, 123 qui, 28+12 parry<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE CODE START--><pre> 
Attacks  Hits        Avg Dmg  Evades            Parries             Misses
148      45 (30.4%)  25.9     13 (8.8%) [8.8%]  67 (49.6%) [45.3%]  23 (33.8%) [15.5%]
</pre><!--EZCODE CODE END--><br>
<br>
Buffed<br>
Merc stats: 312 dex, 216 qui, 28+12 parry<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE CODE START--><pre> 
